item.title: Please! help! theres no one here except me! why?
item.dc:creator: @Snoww Snoww
item.description:
@Snoww wrote:

Okay, basically. Youre on a server that is local to your Computer, IE its just you. a Blank server.

In order to play along with other people, you need to look in the server status page, and choose a server you like the sound of here:

http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php

Once you find one you like the sound of, you get the IP Address by clicking on the link, which is the name of the server.

You then input the IP into the “IP” section on your chosen client. Then you look which port the server uses, and type that into the “Port” Section.

Now just put in your chosen user-name and password, and you should log in.

Good Luck.
